"Books and Authors", ''The New York Times'', 1936-04-12, p. BR12. ProQuest Historical Newspapers The New York Times (1851-2007).</ref><ref name=nyt1941>
"Books and Authors", ''The New York Times'', 1941-02-16, p. BR12. ProQuest Historical Newspapers The New York Times (1851-2007).</ref>。“[[布里尔-津瑟病|布里尔-津瑟病]]”即以他的名字和另一位[[美国|美国]]医生{{link-en|内森·埃德温·布里尔|Nathan Edwin Brill}}的名字命名<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=Definition of Brill-Zinsser disease|url=https://www.medicinenet.com/brill-zinsser_disease/definition.htm|accessdate=2021-02-28|work=MedicineNet|language=en}}</ref>。

